dex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lij1665702652493.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lij1665702652493.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lij1665702652493.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lij1665702652493\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Style\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines the appearance of the split bar. Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Normal</code> (default), <code class=\"ph codeph\">Narrow</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">Thin</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Hidden</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lij1665702652493__section_w1622ab1b5b1_w1623ab1b5_w1624ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"lij1665702652493__table_d12932e1_d12933e1_d12934e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lij1665702652493__table_d12932e1_d12933e1_d12934e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lij1665702652493__table_d12932e1_d12933e1_d12934e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lij1665702652493__table_d12932e1_d12933e1_d12934e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Normal</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lij1665702652493__table_d12932e1_d12933e1_d12934e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Three-dimensional bar with a width of 7 pixels.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lij1665702652493__table_d12932e1_d12933e1_d12934e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Narrow</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lij1665702652493__table_d12932e1_d12933e1_d12934e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Narrower three-dimensional bar.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lij1665702652493__table_d12932e1_d12933e1_d12934e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Thin</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lij1665702652493__table_d12932e1_d12933e1_d12934e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dark gray bar with a width of one pixel.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lij1665702652493__table_d12932e1_d12933e1_d12934e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Hidden</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lij1665702652493__table_d12932e1_d12933e1_d12934e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Bar that is hidden at run time. During development, a hidden bar appears as a dashed line.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lij1665702652493__section_ktt_pqc_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1175106e169\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"lij1665702652493__ul_ts5_qqc_cxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lij1665702652493__li_d42548e1_d42549e1_d42550e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qir1665702652329.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qir1665702652329.html\" title=\"A split bar divides a form or widget horizontally or vertically, making it possible to resize the resulting panes by dragging the split bar or resizing the window. Alternatively, it can be locked to protect an area of the form from being resized or hidden.\">Split Bars</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614353\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614353\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Style Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Style This property determines the appearance of the split bar. Valid values are Normal (default), Narrow , Thin , or Hidden . Value Description Normal Three-dimensional bar with a width of 7 pixels. Narrow Narrower three-dimensional bar. Thin Dark gray bar with a width of one pixel. Hidden Bar that is hidden at run time. During development, a hidden bar appears as a dashed line. Applies To Split Bars Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}